  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/adabdbfd096f5a10ca42c719c5a6c91a.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=73 /></span><br>Pixboy, a mad scientist, finally found a recipe for an ultimate potion. However, malicious dogs destroyed his dreams. Time for revenge!<br><strong>Feel the retro vibes, travel back to the past, enjoy chunky pixels and chiptune music!</strong><br><br><strong>Be agile!</strong><br>Run, jump, soar and avoid deadly obstacles. Don't give up! You will succeed... eventually.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Leave no one behind!</strong><br>Defeat enemies using your super-duper-powerful slingshot. Out of ammo? Jump on foes' heads to defeat them and to get extra bullet!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>(If you feel like a pacifist, spare all the enemies on level and get a special <strong>Pacifist Badge</strong>! But beware: won't be easy!)<br><br><br><strong>Seek for secrets!</strong> <br>Find 'Em all! It's a piece of cake, really...<br>Only 150 secret rooms. Good luck :)<br>Small hint: <span class=\"bb_spoiler\">look for different patterns on walls</span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/c58333071ad0bf7dca012b9f3d27c474.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/c58333071ad0bf7dca012b9f3d27c474.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/c58333071ad0bf7dca012b9f3d27c474.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Meet strange creatures!</strong><br>There are 30 of them. <br>So for now, meet the Fluffy. Fluffy is full of surprises, figuratively and literally.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/df92a3ba9332b9229da83e0cd9de733a.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/df92a3ba9332b9229da83e0cd9de733a.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/df92a3ba9332b9229da83e0cd9de733a.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Tease your mind!</strong><br>Each jump - every mechanism rotates.<br>Plan your way ahead, cause jumping on spikes hurts like hell.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/01a0a4bf3a341e976595204d7f3a5924.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/01a0a4bf3a341e976595204d7f3a5924.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/01a0a4bf3a341e976595204d7f3a5924.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>And now the numbers!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 4 unique worlds with different mechanics inside<br></li><li> 40 hand-crafted levels<br></li><li> 150+ secret rooms<br></li><li> 30 different enemies<br></li><li> 24 retro color palettes<br></li><li> 4 bosses<br></li><li> 4 challenges per level<br></li><li> a Pacifist Badge for sparing all enemies</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/adabdbfd096f5a10ca42c719c5a6c91a.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=73 /></span><br>Pixboy, a mad scientist, finally found a recipe for an ultimate potion. However, malicious dogs destroyed his dreams. Time for revenge!<br><strong>Feel the retro vibes, travel back to the past, enjoy chunky pixels and chiptune music!</strong><br><br><strong>Be agile!</strong><br>Run, jump, soar and avoid deadly obstacles. Don't give up! You will succeed... eventually.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/eb7e132061abc7adffeba6005d74bf34.mp4?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Leave no one behind!</strong><br>Defeat enemies using your super-duper-powerful slingshot. Out of ammo? Jump on foes' heads to defeat them and to get extra bullet!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.poster.avif?t=1651593537\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.webm?t=1651593537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355420/extras/dede53639babc86ce160914a6d421303.mp4?t=1651